<HEADLINE> Nepal, Singapore Agree to Enhance Cooperation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KATHMANDU, April 13 (Xinhua) -- Nepal and Singapore have agreed
to enhance bilateral cooperation between them especially in
sectors of investment, trade and tourism, a joint press communique
said today.
</P>
<P>
The communique, issued at the end of a four-day visit by
Singapore Foreign Minister S. Jayakumar to Nepal, said the two
